name: Ain't No Love In The Heart Of The City (Part III).
description:
The City.

The supposed "Concrete Jungle where dreams are made of".

There's another side.   A side that I personally know very well.  The lights and action contends with the beauty of grime, grit and dimness.  

Growing up, I've been though it all. Doubt, depression. I've broke daylight with shady characters, I've fornicated with the most beautiful, yet foulest of women, I've seen my best friends fall to clutches of demons and drugs and I've survived an assassination attempt via poison.

but the city does have a heart..

it just makes some people too numb to feel it beat.
